==English==
===Verb===
'''[[strike]] [[while]] the [[iron]] is [[hot]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[act]] on an [[opportunity]] [[promptly]]; to avoid [[waiting]].
#:''We should '''strike while the iron is hot''' and order some immediately, before they change the offer.''
